descriptionHtml:
AZEOO is the most effective and optimal application combining Bodybuilding program, Cross Training program and Fitness coaching.



Do you want to lose weight, build muscle 💪 or simply to be Fit 🍏?

Regardless of your level, your weight training program adapts to your personal performance and objectives. Our training focuses on strength, endurance and mobility, with easy to follow sports and nutrition tips.
AZEOO is much more than an application, it is also a great community of thousands of athletes who will support you in every training session through our social network!
Like a real sports coach, AZEOO accompanies you to have a Bodybuilding program adapted to let you become the best version of yourself.

Ready to achieve your goals and exceed your limits? Don't delay your transformation until tomorrow, join AZEOO now!

Exceed YOUR LIMITS


- Getting a flat tummy, developing your Chest? Strength and Mass Gain training programs, weight loss and Sculpt Your Body Programs specifically designed to achieve your objectives!
- Getting curvy Glutes? Lose Weight? Gaining Muscle Mass? AZEOO will guide you: explanations of the weight training exercises to be performed, the number of repetitions to do, the load to use and the rest time to take.
- Glutes and abs, arm or back abs exercises? Select the muscle group to work with more than 50 Bodybuilding workouts designed for a tailor-made workout!
- Improve your favourite movements such as Bench Press, Squat or Abs exercises? More than 500 videos of exercises & Crossfit, described step by step, for an easy, optimal and safe practice.
- Crossfit enthusiast? find hundreds of WOD, join battles between athletes and become unstoppable 😱
- Create your own Bodybuilding and Crossfit programming with our Bodybuilding app editor, and share them with your friends 👍!

YOUR SPORTS COACHING / FITNESS AT ANY TIME


- Analyze your progress by accessing the statistics of your Bodybuilding and Fitness program.

- Push Pull Legs

AZEOO is the most effective and optimal application combining Gym Workouts plan, Cross Training plan and Fitness coaching.



Do you want to lose weight, build muscle 💪 or simply to be Fit 🍏?

Regardless of your level, your weight training program adapts to your personal performance and objectives. Our training focuses on strength, endurance and mobility, with easy to follow sports and nutrition tips.
AZEOO is much more than an application, it is also a great community of thousands of athletes who will support you in every training session through our social network!
Like a real sports coach, AZEOO accompanies you to have a Workouts & Training plan at Home or Gym adapted to let you become the best version of yourself.

Ready to achieve your goals and exceed your limits? Don't delay your transformation until tomorrow, join AZEOO now!

Exceed YOUR LIMITS


- Getting a flat tummy, developing your Chest? Strength and Mass Gain training programs, weight loss and Sculpt Your Body Programs specifically designed to achieve your objectives!
- Getting curvy Glutes? Lose Weight? Gaining Muscle Mass? AZEOO will guide you: explanations of the weight training exercises to be performed, the number of repetitions to do, the load to use and the rest time to take.
- Glutes and abs, arm or back abs exercises? Select the muscle group to work with more than 50 Gym workouts designed for a tailor-made workout!
- Improve your favourite movements such as Bench Press, Squat or Abs exercises? More than 500 videos of exercises & Crossfit, described step by step, for an easy, optimal and safe practice.
- Crossfit enthusiast? find hundreds of WOD, join battles between athletes and become unstoppable 😱
- Create your own Bodybuilding, Crossfit and Fitness plan with our Workouts app editor, and share them with your friends 👍!

YOUR SPORTS COACHING / FITNESS AT ANY TIME


- Analyze your progress by accessing the statistics of your Workouts & Training plan at Home or Gym.
- Break your personal records.
- track your training

Get Workouts (500+) and Bodybuilding / Cross training / Fitness Plans such as :


- Push Pull Legs
- Full Body
- Half Body
- Minimum Equipment
- Build Muscle
- Lose Weight
- Sculpt Your Body
- German Volume Training
- German Volume Training Optimised
- Chest Intensification
- Back Intensification
- Arms Intensification
- Shoulders Intensification
- 30 days of training Challenge without any equipment!

TOGETHER, LET’S STAY MOTIVATED!


- Meet and train with athletes who aspire to the same goal as you.
- Set yourself even more ambitious fitness challenges. Exceed your limits!
- Share your training and achievements freely.
- Encourage and be encouraged by thousands of athletes.
- Be proud of your progress: share your Before / After photos to become a real source of inspiration!

STAY CONNECTED WITH YOUR GYM!


- Be informed of the latest news from your gym in real time.
- Let yourself be guided by your sports coach who will follow your evolution step by step on the Bodybuilding App.

JOIN US FROM NOW!

💪🍏
And start your transformation with the BEST Gym Workouts & Fitness App ! 👍💪💪
